    <h1>Press About the Project – Bednarczyk</h1><br />
    <p>
      The legacy of Krystyna Bednarczyk and her Poets’ and Painters’ Press
      continues to inspire researchers, literary enthusiasts, and artists alike.
      Our project, dedicated to unveiling her contributions to Polish and
      British cultural heritage, has garnered significant attention from
      academic circles and the press. Below, we highlight key publications and
      articles reflecting on Bednarczyk’s remarkable impact.
    </p>
